{"type":null,"faqId":38485,"title":"通过 WLAN 直连传输数据","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">无需接入点，使用 WLAN 直连可以直接连接两台设备，快速传输文件。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125358\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">此功能仅适用于华为设备之间的数据传输。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><a name=\"_task_connect_devices-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> 连接两台设备</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125359\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在使用 WLAN 直连传输数据前，请确保两台设备都已开启 WLAN 直连功能。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在主屏幕，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125360\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">“设置”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">在“全部设置”页签下，点击 “WLAN”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击 “WLAN” 开关，开启 WLAN。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击 “WLAN 直连”，开启 WLAN 直连功能。手机将搜索出可用设备。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击要连接的设备。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">2.</span><a name=\"_task_send_data_wifi-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">通过 WLAN 直连发送文件</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">长按要发送的文件，点击“分享 &gt; WLAN 直连”，手机将自动搜索出可用设备。然后点击要接收文件的设备。</span></span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">3.</span><a name=\"_task_receive_data_wifi-chtext\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">通过 WLAN 直连接收文件</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">手机通过 WLAN 直连收文件时，界面会弹出“文件传输”对话框。点击“接收”，即可接收文件。打开通知面板，点击“通知”，可以查看文件接收进度。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 10.5pt; \">接收的文件默认存储在“文件管理”的 “WLAN 直连” 文件夹内。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3765","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441442758000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":96,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"通过 WLAN 直连传输数据","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}